</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Dyson 宣傳片洩密，證實 VISNAV 掃地機械人存在</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/27/dyson-visnav/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=dyson-visnav</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 27 May 2022 11:14:18 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Dyson]]></category><category><![CDATA[VISNAV]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1101954</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Dyson 早前公開的宣傳片暗藏了多個細節，除了公開各款機器人的原型機外，在首席工程師 Jake Dyson  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Dyson 早前公開的宣傳片暗藏了多個細節，除了公開各款機器人的原型機外，在首席工程師 Jake Dyson 進入實驗室前，影到牆上掛有寫著「VISNAV」的海報。由於在「VISNAV」海報附近的都時歷代的掃地機械人海報，分別為 DC06、360 Eye 及 Heurist，令人推測 VISNAV 是 Dyson 即將推出的掃地機械人。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ddc4bf10-dcdb-11ec-8def-4b6d0b9a9a63.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ddc4bf10-dcdb-11ec-8def-4b6d0b9a9a63-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ddc4bf10-dcdb-11ec-8def-4b6d0b9a9a63-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ddc4bf10-dcdb-11ec-8def-4b6d0b9a9a63-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ddc4bf10-dcdb-11ec-8def-4b6d0b9a9a63-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ddc4bf10-dcdb-11ec-8def-4b6d0b9a9a63-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ddc4bf10-dcdb-11ec-8def-4b6d0b9a9a63.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：Engadget</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">早於去年時，有人於曾於 FCC 網站中看到印有「Dyson 360 Hyperdymium」字樣的掃地機器人相片，因此外界推算 VISNAV 可能是 Dyson 360 Hyperdymium 的代號。從相片可見，半橢圓形的 VISNAV 與 360 Eye 及 Heurist 的圓形設計明顯不同，而集塵筒及滾筒刷則分別設於機身的前後。外界估計，VISNAV 一字帶有視覺導航（Vision Navigation）的意思。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/48efbe70-dcdc-11ec-bd37-6793a9e8ec3d.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/48efbe70-dcdc-11ec-bd37-6793a9e8ec3d-694x451.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="451" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/48efbe70-dcdc-11ec-bd37-6793a9e8ec3d-694x451.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/48efbe70-dcdc-11ec-bd37-6793a9e8ec3d-1280x833.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/48efbe70-dcdc-11ec-bd37-6793a9e8ec3d-768x500.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/48efbe70-dcdc-11ec-bd37-6793a9e8ec3d-1536x999.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/48efbe70-dcdc-11ec-bd37-6793a9e8ec3d.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：Engadget</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">此外，宣傳片亦疑似錄到測試掃地機器人的情況，由於 Dyson 特意以馬賽克處理有關掃地機器人，令觀眾無法得知更多細節。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/6a444e60-dcdc-11ec-97bb-7d0e589f82e7.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1101988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/6a444e60-dcdc-11ec-97bb-7d0e589f82e7-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/6a444e60-dcdc-11ec-97bb-7d0e589f82e7-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/6a444e60-dcdc-11ec-97bb-7d0e589f82e7-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/6a444e60-dcdc-11ec-97bb-7d0e589f82e7-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/6a444e60-dcdc-11ec-97bb-7d0e589f82e7-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/6a444e60-dcdc-11ec-97bb-7d0e589f82e7.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694